She heard Phobia.  "He is not hired help." She looked at Drillbit and 
smiled.  
"Yeah, he is right though, there is a fight out  there taht we need 
to deal with."
She didn't realize that Drillbit couldn't hear Phobia.  
She slid off the table and kissed Drillbit's cheek.  Come on, let's 
show those maximals they can't push us around."  She smiled at him.
